data.name: DragSourceDragEvent
desc: The DragSourceDragEvent is delivered from an object that implements the XDragSourceContext to the currently registered drag source listener.
It contains state regarding the current state of the operation to enable the operations initiator to provide the end user with the appropriate drag over feedback.

items.name: DropAction
lines: The drag action selected by the current drop target.

items.name: UserAction
lines: The user's currently selected drop action.
